  "3075410": {
    "name": "命运之手：人各有命",
    "steam_appid": 3075410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/b8688ccd7c094587d68d97b4c2f019c2.avif?t=1772186294\" width=616 height=192 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发牌人曾经是一个强大的法师，为了无限期地保存自己的生命，他向死神的代表发起了一场挑战。从那以后，他统治着生死游戏，他奋战不息，终获自由。然而在这过程中，他失去了所有力量，于是每分每秒都在谋划着复仇之日。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将通过黑暗而复杂的法术，前往虚空，那是生死界限之外的维度。无人能完好无损地抵达虚空。你的记忆也变得支离破碎，就连发牌人也被剥夺了生死棋局的掌控之力......这一次不是为了玩生死游戏，而是要训练一位新的挑战者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们将携手借助卡牌的力量，一步步找回记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/e7459147c60b99af88f452498df58644.poster.avif?t=1772186294\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/e7459147c60b99af88f452498df58644.webm?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/e7459147c60b99af88f452498df58644.mp4?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/8f0a1ccee717cffd329805520d400b41.avif?t=1772186294\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过牌组触发的文字遭遇与任务，可解锁代币并获取新卡牌，每一局结束后，你的可能性与力量都将无限扩展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索隐藏遭遇结局，获取能重塑装备的强力附魔，让力量分化出全新路径，打造独特流派与玩法风格。基于每局抽到的卡牌与你的抉择，每次冒险都将焕发崭新面貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/d3f5a77197913dc15bacc8a2af1ef02f.poster.avif?t=1772186294\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/d3f5a77197913dc15bacc8a2af1ef02f.webm?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/d3f5a77197913dc15bacc8a2af1ef02f.mp4?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/d8294429cf53179ac0790cc8546cb575.avif?t=1772186294\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败蜂拥而至的小怪，升级你的装备，深入探索《命运之手》的世界。收集并组合各种毁灭性的武器和附魔！在快节奏的激战中向接踵而至的恐怖怪物释放地狱之火。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/a0001301a9c4f064f111f0858c2d3633.poster.avif?t=1772186294\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/a0001301a9c4f064f111f0858c2d3633.webm?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/a0001301a9c4f064f111f0858c2d3633.mp4?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/59bb521a2b6b5097e2a2edc037af0da5.avif?t=1772186294\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁来自《命运之手》宇宙的多位英雄，每位英雄皆配备专属自动射击武器与增益卡牌，为每次冒险的牌组构筑增添无限可能。每位英雄皆配备独特可激活装备卡，能在战斗中扭转战局，塑造专属战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/f589e2d38392c18e8d454de8467387c5.poster.avif?t=1772186294\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/f589e2d38392c18e8d454de8467387c5.webm?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/f589e2d38392c18e8d454de8467387c5.mp4?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/a7fb82b92c3319d4ecfbd76cda81fa50.avif?t=1772186294\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前所未有的俯视角自动射击，探索全新及重制的遭遇战与装备，游历未知地域，并操控命运之手宇宙中的经典英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战前所未有的规模——命运之手敌军与怪物将如潮水般席卷而来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/51a2d837d25f7d21926535f1043ecb61.poster.avif?t=1772186294\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/51a2d837d25f7d21926535f1043ecb61.webm?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/51a2d837d25f7d21926535f1043ecb61.mp4?t=1772186294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075410/extras/f6608576e77ad849285fc9f8ff494207.avif?t=1772186294\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请加入QQ群：975061614。参与这场冒险，与创作者并肩，见证庄家归来，亲历魔法重生时刻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
